[Implementation - MCP 整合指南]
配置 MCP 增強測試：

1. MCP 配置檔案：
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "playwright": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@modelcontextprotocol/server-playwright"],
      "env": {
        "PLAYWRIGHT_HEADLESS": "false"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

2. AI 驅動測試生成：
```javascript
